%F A029318 a(n) = a(n-3)+a(n-8)+a(n-9)-a(n-11)-a(n-15)-a(n-17)-a(n-21)+a(n-23)+a(n-24)+a(n-29)-a(n-32). - _Wesley Ivan Hurt_, Apr 22 2021
%F A029318 a(n) = floor((n^3+24*n^2-132*n+5184)/15552 + ((n+2) mod 3)*(n^2+32*n+216)/648 - ((2*n^2+n) mod 3)*n/81 + ((n mod 4)-2)^2*n/192). - _Hoang Xuan Thanh_, Apr 12 2026
